post.videoDescription:
Listen to and/or order my debut album here: http://music.iancanderson.com

My acoustic cover version of Duncan Sheik's 1997 hit "Barely Breathing."

New Seagull S6 Original guitar, recorded through a mid-side stereo setup (CAD M179 and Oktava MK012), vocals recorded with MXL 990.  

Audio interface: RME Fireface 800
DAW: Cockos Reaper 3.0
